  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Our class visited a real farm today, and within five minutes, a cow was staring directly at Bernice like it wanted to steal her lunch.",
      "zh": "我們班今天去了一座真正的農場，才五分鐘，一頭乳牛就直直盯著 Bernice 看，好像想搶她的午餐。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The farmer showed us how to feed the pigs, and William, who joined this trip because his class combined with ours for the day, got mud on his shoes almost immediately.",
      "zh": "農夫教我們怎麼餵豬，而 William（因為他們班今天跟我們班合併校外教學）幾乎立刻鞋子上就沾了泥巴。"
    },
    {
      "en": "There was a small horse in the far field, and the farmer let a few brave students take turns feeding it a handful of hay.",
      "zh": "遠處的田裡有一匹小馬，農夫讓幾個勇敢的學生輪流餵牠一把乾草。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A group of hens made a loud, constant noise near the barn, and one hen in particular seemed determined to follow Bernice everywhere she walked.",
      "zh": "一群母雞在穀倉附近發出又大聲又不間斷的叫聲，其中一隻母雞特別堅持要跟著 Bernice 走到哪跟到哪。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William found a tiny lamb resting quietly in the shade and declared it the softest thing he had ever touched in his entire life.",
      "zh": "William 發現一隻在陰影裡安靜休息的小羊，宣布這是他這輩子摸過最柔軟的東西。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The farmer explained that raising farm animals takes a lot of patience, since every single one needs food, water, and attention every single day.",
      "zh": "農夫解釋養農場動物需要很大的耐心，因為每一隻動物每天都需要食物、水，還有關注。"
    },
    {
      "en": "One boy got bitten lightly by a curious goat while trying to feed it, and he wore the small mark like a badge of honor for the rest of the day.",
      "zh": "有個男生在餵一隻好奇的山羊時被輕輕咬了一口，他接下來一整天都把那個小小的痕跡當成榮譽勳章一樣炫耀。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Near the barn, there was a small fire pit where the farmer's family cooks dinner outside during warmer months.",
      "zh": "穀倉附近有一個小小的生火坑，農夫一家在天氣暖和的月份會在戶外用它煮晚餐。"
    },
    {
      "en": "We could see thin smoke rising from a nearby chimney, and the farmer said the heat from that stove keeps the whole house warm in winter.",
      "zh": "我們可以看到附近煙囪冒出一縷細細的煙，農夫說那個爐子的熱氣冬天能讓整間屋子保持溫暖。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice, still being followed by her new hen friend, decided to name it \"Diary,\" saying it deserved a name as ordinary as the rest of our lives.",
      "zh": "還在被那隻母雞跟著的 Bernice，決定幫牠取名叫「Diary」，說牠值得一個跟我們生活一樣平凡的名字。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William begged the farmer to let him take the lamb home, and the farmer very kindly explained that lambs need a whole field, not a small apartment.",
      "zh": "William 拜託農夫讓他把小羊帶回家，農夫很和善地解釋小羊需要一整片田地，不是一間小公寓。"
    },
    {
      "en": "On the bus ride back, William talked nonstop about the lamb, the hens, and the goat that bit his classmate, in that exact order, twice.",
      "zh": "回程公車上，William 一路不停講小羊、母雞，還有咬他同學的那隻山羊，就照這個順序，講了兩遍。"
    }
  ],
